modName: Adiriel - Female High Elf Altmer Save - Lvl 1
descriptionHtml:
Adiriel is a lvl 1 Altmer woman located at Riverwood, ready to save the world! Or perhaps to fail in the first fight against a bear. ;)


Download the file and unzip it to your Saves folder: DocumentsMyGamesSkyrimSaves.
If you wish to change some details just type showracemenu in the console.


She looks like this using the following mods (they are not necessary but recommended):
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=498]High Quality Eyes[/url]
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4307]AOF Believable Hair[/url]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563]Coverwomen Look #1[/url]
author: Finduilas80
